en: Accessible to skateboards, roller-skates and scooters, the Skatepark of Rouen offers 1,500 sq m dedicated to your favourite sports. Skateboard, roller-skate and scooter lessons for different ability levels are scheduled every week, and supervised by qualified instructors.
